# ---- nk-frontend environment ----
# IMPORTANT: Vite only exposes variables that start with VITE_, and it bakes
# them into the build at BUILD TIME (not runtime).
#
# LOCAL DEV: copy this file to ".env" and leave VITE_API_URL blank — Vite's
# dev proxy forwards /api to http://localhost:4000 (see vite.config.js).
#
# PRODUCTION (AWS Amplify): do NOT rely on a committed file. Set VITE_API_URL
# in the Amplify Console → App settings → Environment variables, to your
# backend (App Runner) URL with NO trailing slash, e.g.
#   https://abcd1234.us-east-1.awsapprunner.com
# Then redeploy so the build picks it up.

VITE_API_URL=
